  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_secure_training_centre">Secure Training Centre</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisation</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_secure_training_centre">Secure Training Centre</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_secure_training_centre">STC</xref>
) is a type of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_detention_accommodation">Youth Detention Accommodation</xref>
 that accommodates young offenders between the ages of 12-17.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on Health and Justice healthcare, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/commissioning/health-just/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Health and Justice</xref>
.  </p>

